== 一般合規 ==
根据国内税收法第501章节，一个501(c)组织必须为不相关业务收入（即从该组织免税范围以外的事务中获得的收入）纳税<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unrelated_Business_Income_Tax |title=Unrelated Business Income Tax |accessdate=2009-10-10 |archive-date=2009-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090530135408/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unrelated_Business_Income_Tax |dead-url=no }}</ref>， 无论它是否从中[[盈利|盈利]]，但这不包括出售获赠物品、由志愿者进行的商业交易或从某些宾果游戏<ref>Bingo Games,美国国内税收法 (Internal Revenue Code) [http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/513%28f%29.html § 513(f)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/513%28f%29.html |date=20100110084057 }}条款中定义的与宾果游戏规则和过程相似的商业活动</ref>中获得的收入。出售价值超过2500美元的捐赠物或接受价值超过5000美元捐赠物可能需要特别申请和备案。

注意"免税"并没有免除组织维护税务档案和填写税务表格<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tax_return_%28United_States%29 |title=Tax returns |accessdate=2009-10-10 |archive-date=2009-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091014014211/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tax_return_(United_States) |dead-url=no }}</ref>的义务。<ref>例如国内税收法[http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6033.html § 6033] {{Wayback|url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6033.html |date=20091124021512 }}和[http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6050L.html § 6050(L)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6050L.html |date=20090303043428 }}条款中规定的组织需要填写的税务文件</ref>在以前，每年总收入低于25000美元的组织一般不需要填写年度纳税表格<ref>Internal Revenue Bulletin 23, 1982, exercising国内税收法[http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6033(a)(2)(B).html § 6033(a)(2)(B)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6033(a)(2)(B).html |date=20080919044122 }}</ref>；但从2008年开始，许多这样的组织必须每年填写一份叫做"电子明信片"（{{lang|en|e-Postcard}}）的税务文件，否则可能失去免税资格。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.irs.gov/charities/article/0,,id=169250,00.html |title=Annual Electronic Filing Requirement for Small Exempt Organizations—Form 990-N (e-Postcard) |publisher=Irs.gov |date= |accessdate=2009-05-28 |archive-date=2009-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505232725/http://www.irs.gov/charities/article/0,,id=169250,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

没有填写美国国税局990表（享受所得税减免的组织税务表, {{lang|en|Return of Organization Exempt From Income Tax}}）之类税务表格的组织可能遭受每年最多250,000美元罚款。免税组织和政治组织（不包括教堂和相似宗教机构）必须公开税务表格、报告和相关免税文件以供公众查阅。

公众可以通过前往组织办公室，邮寄附有复映材料费用的书面请求或直接通过4506-A表 （供公众查阅或复制的政治组织税务表, {{lang|en|Request for Public Inspection or Copy or Political Organization IRS Form}}）向填写国税局990表格 （或类似表格如990-EZ, 990-PF）的免税组织查询其过去三个税务年的990表。4506-A表还允许公众查阅或复制免税组织的1023表（免税待遇申请表, {{lang|en|Application for Recognition of Exemption}}）或1024表、8871表 （政治组织527条款状态公告, {{lang|en|Political Organization Notice of Section 527 Status}}）和8872表 （政治组织接受献金和开支表, {{lang|en|Political Organization Report of Contribution and Expenditures}}）。

联邦法律要求免税组织必须填写这样的表格并向公众开放。<ref>国内税收法[http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6652.html § 6652] {{Wayback|url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6652.html |date=20091001035612 }}和[http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6104.html § 6164] {{Wayback|url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/26/6104.html |date=20091022040017 }}条款</ref>

